# Dependencies

See requirements.txt - M2Crypto requires swig on OSX: `brew install swig` and openSSL: `brew install swig`
		     - required >v0.15 version of pyOpenSSL


Server:
----------

Server written in python.
Satisfies all project requirements.
Further features include:
	Random number challenge to verify clients identity on vouch

Certificates should be placed in server/db/certificates/
Files should be placed in server/db/files/
All users should have a self-signed certificate present to help with chain verification.
tests/server/main.py 	runs a series of tests on the server.
	
To run server:
	python runserver.py -ip <IP to listen>


Client:
--------

Client written in Java. 
Satisfies all project requirements.

Deviation from project spec:
	Server/client certificates are needed in the working directory.
	See client/CLIENT-NOTES for full details.

To build client:
	cd client
	./build.sh
	java -jar oldTrustyClient ....args


